        <div style="color: white; font-family: sans-serif;"><strong>Hurry! Trip leaving soon!</strong></div>
        <% else %>
        <div style="color: white; font-family: sans-serif;"><strong>Plenty of time left before trip. Get some coffee.</strong></div><br>
        <% end %>
